n subset support:\n  - `*/N * * * *` — every N minutes\n  - `0 * * * *` — every hour on the hour\n  - `0 0 * * *` — every day at midnight\n- API: Create, remove, list active schedules\n- Manual \"tick\"/\"check\" evaluates schedules and enqueues due tasks (for testing)\n- Recurring tasks → regular tasks subject to all queue rules\n- Removing schedule → stops future occurrences\n\n#### Phase 11: Middleware Pipeline (`/workspace/phases/phase-11.md`)\n- Register middleware functions per queue\n- Task passes through middleware in order before handler\n- Middleware receives task and \"next\" function\n- Not calling \"next\" → skip task processing\n- Middleware can modify task (metadata, transform payload)\n- Middleware throws error → task marked failed\n- Processing function/handler registered per queue, invoked after middleware\n- Each queue has independent middleware stack\n\n#### Phase 12: Graceful Shutdown (`/workspace/phases/phase-12.md`)\n- Shutdown signals stop accepting new tasks\n- Adding tasks after shutdown → error\n- Wait for currently-processing tasks to finish (configurable timeout)\n- Timeout exceeded → force-cancel tasks\n- API: Register callbacks during shutdown\n- Shutdown summary: completed count, force-cancelled count, duration\n- Multiple shutdown calls → safe and return same result\n- No processing tasks → complete immediately\n\n---\n\n### Test Configuration (`/workspace/.thunderdome/rubric.yaml`)\n\n**Total: 90 tests, 90 points**\n- 8 tests × Phase 1 (8 pts)\n- 7 tests × Phases 2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 11 (6 phases × 7 pts = 42 pts)\n- 8 tests × Phases 3, 5, 7, 9, 12 (5 phases × 8 pts = 40 pts)\n\n**Validation**:\n- Test: `npm test` (exit code 0)\n- Build: `npm run build` (exit code 0)\n- Lint: `npm run lint` (exit code 0)\n\n**Scoring**: Per-test basis, 1 point per passing test. Pass threshold: 90 points (100%).\n\n---\n\n### Current State\n\n- **Source Directory**: `/workspace/src/` is empty (.gitkeep only) — ready for implementation\n- **Git Status**: N